metatags.og:description:
Hi, I'm Leonard Yankelovich, the Founder and Owner of DARTZ Motorz and FREZE EV. My journey in the automotive industry began when I inherited a minority stake in the German-Dutch JV RBVZ in Riga from my great-grandfather. In 1988, I revived RBVZ JV as DARTZ, a controversial luxury armored vehicle brand that has since become a leading force in the luxury vehicle industry. Building on this success, I also resurrected Frese & C⁰ as FREZE EV in 2020, producing high-end, sustainable electric vehicles for environmentally conscious consumers. I'm passionate about innovative, high-quality vehicles that cater to the needs of modern consumers, and I'm excited to continue pushing the boundaries of the automotive industry with my team.
